text: Emin Ahmadov (born 6 October 1986) is an Azerbaijani wrestler. He won the bronze medal at the 2012 Summer Olympics in the Greco-Roman men's 74 kg event. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Azerbaijani wrestlers Category:Olympic bronze medalists Category:Medalists at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Olympians for Azerbaijan Category:21st-century Azerbaijani people
